name: ST305 Uni Fashion
descriptionDK: &nbspQuality: 100% combed and enzyme washed cottonOxford Grey: 85% combed cotton, 15% viscoseHeather Black: 65% combed cotton, 35% polyesterAnthracite: 60 % combed cotton, 40% polyesterWeight: 165 g/m²Single jerseyBox: 50 pcs., pack: 10 pcs.The product is LABELFREE and contains only a small size label in the left side of the neck.The ST305 Uni Fashion is a classic t-shirt with a slightly fitted cut and side seam. The sleeve is tailored to fit this cut.Sleeves and bottom are hemmed with 3 threaded flatlock. 3 threaded flatlock make a decorative detail to the T-shirt. It has 3 straight stitches with zig-zag stitches between on the right side of the T-shirt, it makes the hem more visible than with a normal twin-needle stitching.The neckline is finished with at 1x1 cotton rib and stitched whit at twin needle topstitch.The t-shirt is made from one of our most popular cotton fabrics, single jersey 165 g / m². We use this material for most of our t-shirts. The material is known for the following qualities: soft, flexible, hardwearing, suitable for many washing, good color fastness, minimal shrinkage, smooth and uniform surface.The t-shirt has neck tape and only a small size label in the left side of the neck. In the left side seam, there is a small label with the product name and washing instructions.

name: ST1000 Face Mask 3-ply
descriptionDK: &nbspSave up to 50% on all facemasks. When buying 2500+ fabric masks you save 50%The discount will be deducted manually on your next invoice.The Danish authorities demand that people wear face masks in public in Denmark. There is no requirement for them to be CE approved or medical. Read our face mask guide click here.We can now offer 3-layer reusable fabric face masks, which can be washed at 60°CInner layer: Mesh, 100% polyesterMiddle layer: Single jersey, 100% cottonOuter layer: Isoli, 65% cotton / 35% polyesterCoated metal nose clip which is sewn into the maskAdjustable straps for the ears (13 cm.)Washable at 60°CSuitable for printingNot for medical useNot personal protective equipmentWe recommend that you wash the mask before useRead the test report here&nbspWe have chosen to use 3 different materials for ST1000 Face Mask, each layer has its own quality.The inner layer is mesh, which is often used for sportswear as it helps to conduct moisture away from the body, and in this case, away from your face.In the middle, there is a layer of single jersey that helps to absorb and retain moisture.The outer layer is a brushed isoli where the inside absorbs moisture and the outside prevents moisture from penetrating.It has a round shape over the nose and mouth to provide a spacious fit. It shapes around the chin and fits well on both large and small faces.The edge is finished with mesh piping which is soft against the skin. The piping continues and turns into ear straps.The ear straps have a soft plastic bead that holds the straps in place.&nbspThe nose clip helps to keep the mask in place and close to the nose. This is an advantage especially if you wear glasses, so they do not fog up.
